odata.msgraph.client.beta.entity

Class AppleUserInitiatedEnrollmentProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • odata.msgraph.client.beta.entity.Entity
      • odata.msgraph.client.beta.entity.AppleUserInitiatedEnrollmentProfile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ODataEntityType, ODataType

    public class AppleUserInitiatedEnrollmentProfile
extends Entity
implements ODataEntityType
    “The enrollmentProfile resource represents a collection of configurations which must be provided pre-enrollment to enable enrolling certain devices whose identities have been pre-staged. Pre-staged device identities are assigned to this type of profile to apply the profile's configurations at enrollment of the corresponding device.”
